      <item>
        <title>扫描仪，胶卷和小众软件</title>
        <link>http://nianze.tk/zh/posts/2020/01/2020-01-18-delta-hp5-and-vuescan/</link>
        <pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2020 14:28:45 -0500</pubDate>
        <author>daoxinzhishui@gmail.com (刀心水)</author>
        <guid>http://nianze.tk/zh/posts/2020/01/2020-01-18-delta-hp5-and-vuescan/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;之前在eBay上淘的&lt;a href=&#34;https://imaging.nikon.com/lineup/scanner/coolscan_4/index.htm&#34;&gt;尼康COOLSCAN IV ED (LS-40 ED)&lt;/a&gt;和SA-21 Adapter昨晚总算到了。迫不及待的想试试看扫描出来的效果，却发现驱动软件成了大问题。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;heading&#34;&gt;扫描仪&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;figure &gt;
  
    
